

# Code Examples for Test Automation Training with Robot Framework & Playwright

# --- Day 1: Introduction & Basics ---

# Example 1: Running Your First Test
*** Settings ***
Library    Browser

*** Test Cases ***
Open Google and Search
    [Documentation]    Open Google and perform a search
    New Browser    browser=chromium    headless=False
    New Page    https://www.google.com
    Fill Text    input[name="q"]    Robot Framework
    Press Keys    input[name="q"]    ENTER
    Wait For Elements State    css=search    visible
    Close Browser

# Example 2: Test Case Structure
*** Settings ***
Library    Browser

*** Variables ***
${URL}    https://www.google.com

*** Test Cases ***
Open Google and Close
    Open Browser    ${URL}    chrome
    Close Browser

# --- Day 2: Intermediate Concepts & Best Practices ---

# Example 3: Using Variables
*** Variables ***
${URL}    https://www.example.com
${BROWSER}    chromium
${SEARCH_TERM}    Robot Framework

*** Test Cases ***
Open Example Page
    New Browser    browser=${BROWSER}    headless=False
    New Page    ${URL}
    Close Browser

# Example 4: Custom Keywords & Functions
*** Keywords ***
Open Web Page
    [Arguments]    ${url}
    New Browser    browser=chromium    headless=False
    New Page    ${url}

Search for Term
    [Arguments]    ${query}
    Fill Text    input[name="q"]    ${query}
    Press Keys    input[name="q"]    ENTER
    Wait For Elements State    css=search    visible

*** Test Cases ***
Perform Search
    Open Web Page    https://www.google.com
    Search for Term    ${SEARCH_TERM}
    Close Browser

# Example 5: Data-Driven Testing with Test Templates
*** Test Cases ***
Search Multiple Terms
    [Template]    Search Google
    Robot Framework
    Playwright Library
    Test Automation
    Web Scraping

*** Keywords ***
Search Google
    [Arguments]    ${query}
    New Browser    browser=chromium    headless=False
    New Page    https://www.google.com
    Fill Text    input[name="q"]    ${query}
    Press Keys    input[name="q"]    ENTER
    Close Browser

# Example 6: Assertions & Validations
*** Test Cases ***
Verify Page Title
    New Browser    browser=chromium    headless=False
    New Page    https://www.example.com
    ${title}    Get Title
    Should Be Equal    ${title}    Example Domain
    Close Browser

# --- Day 3: Advanced Topics & Project Work ---

# Example 7: Handling Dynamic & Complex Elements
*** Test Cases ***
Handle Dynamic Content
    New Browser    browser=chromium    headless=False
    New Page    https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/dynamic_loading/1
    Click    css=#start button
    Wait For Elements State    css=#finish    visible    timeout=10s
    ${text}    Get Text    css=#finish
    Should Be Equal    ${text}    Hello World!
    Close Browser

# Example 8: Running Tests in CI/CD Pipelines
name: Run Robot Tests

on: [push]

jobs:
  test:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout repository
        uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - name: Setup Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v4
        with:
          python-version: '3.9'
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: |
          pip install robotframework
          pip install robotframework-browser
          rfbrowser init
      - name: Run tests
        run: |
          robot tests/

# Example 9: Debugging & Troubleshooting
*** Test Cases ***
Debugging Example
    New Browser    browser=chromium    headless=False
    New Page    https://www.google.com
    Set Screenshot Directory    ${OUTPUT_DIR}
    Capture Page Screenshot    debug_screenshot.png
    Close Browser

